  "full_text": "An update for Red is now available for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 10.\n\nRed Hat Ceph Storage is a scalable, open, software-defined storage platform that combines the most stable version of the Ceph storage system with a Ceph management platform, deployment utilities, and support services.These new packages include numerous enhancements and bug fixes. Space precludes documenting all of these changes in this advisory. Users are directed to the Red Hat Ceph Storage Release Notes for information on the most significant of these changes:https://docs.redhat.com/en/documentation/red_hat_ceph_storage/7/html/7.1_release_notes"
}